# RBAC Guard Prosedürü

## Step 1: Yetki Matrisi

`Docs/07_SECURITY_IMPLEMENTATION.md` §5.3 ve `Docs/03_API_CONTRACTS.md` endpoint başlığındaki rol notu.

## Step 2: Backend Guard

```python
@router.delete("/sources/{source_id}", dependencies=[Depends(require_admin)])
```

Viewer read-only endpoint'lerde yalnızca `get_current_user`.

## Step 3: Service Katmanı (defense in depth)

Kritik işlemde servis başında rol assert (opsiyonel, router yeterli değilse).

## Step 4: Frontend

Admin nav item `RoleGate`; route middleware `/admin/*`.

## Step 5: Test (zorunlu)

```python
async def test_viewer_cannot_delete_source(viewer_client):
    resp = await viewer_client.delete(f"/api/v1/sources/{id}")
    assert resp.status_code == 403
    assert resp.json()["error"]["code"] == "FORBIDDEN"
```

## Step 6: Docs

- [ ] `Docs/03` endpoint rol notu
- [ ] `Docs/06` admin ekran permission (varsa)

